The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Molest bid with biscuits
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     Molest bid with biscuits
                            
	Hyderabad, June 16 (PTI): A six-year-old girl has told her parents that the driver of her school bus undressed in front of her and asked her to strip after giving her some biscuits.         
	The girl, who was the last to be dropped from school, said she was slapped when she refused to obey.         
	The incident came to light today when the girls parents lodged a complaint after she narrated the incident, said deputy commissioner of police, M. Kantha Rao.        
	The police have picked up three persons  the driver, the conductor and a guard of the school.         
	The driver denied he had assaulted the girl, claiming his friends had tried to molest her.                                                                                                                                                                         
